                                <div class="goDigitalLeftPane left">
                                    <div class="contentTitle">
                                        Enjoy compatibility with different digital devices</div>
                                    <div class="contentLeft">
                                        Access your TFC content through the online gadget of your choice with TFC.tv’s compatibility
                                        with Windows, Apple and Linux operating systems.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="goDigitalRightPane">
                                    <!-- <div class="contentRight">
                                        Learn more about device compatibility</div>
