                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="contentContainer">
                                <div class="goDigitalLeftPane left">
                                    <div class="contentTitle">
                                        Get rewarded for regular activity and purchase</div>
                                    <div class="contentLeft">
                                        See the difference of using the official platform of TFC with TFC.tv’s Badging feature,
                                        which automatically entitles you to our system of free credits, content and other
                                        exclusive treats.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="goDigitalRightPane">
                                    <!-- <div class="contentRight">
                                       Learn more about TFC.tv Badges</div> -->
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="contentContainer">
                                <div class="goDigitalLeftPane left">
                                    <div class="contentTitle">
                                        Learn more from an extensive product knowledgebase</div>
                                    <div class="contentLeft">
                                        Find the find information you need about TFC.tv in our Help Center, where you can
